Assumption:
 the linear program has inner radius 
\begin_inset Formula $r$
\end_inset

,
 outer radius 
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

 and Lipschitz constant 
\begin_inset Formula $L$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

